tweet: A9: Robocallers can “spoof” phone numbers to make it look like a call is coming from a govt agency.   Govt officials will never: • call & ask for sensitive info like your social security number, • demand payment through gift cards, or • threaten you. #SlamTheScamChat #NCPW2022
